snippet.textDisplay:
When u sit alone and process the song. It's not about separation from the person you love. You both are not together anymore but both of you wish well for each other. The verse " Jaunga kahan" states that there is no one except the other significant person and that you will always come back to them.
Things are not well right now cause the situation is not right, the timing is not right. But we both will grow in our individual lives, find peace in ourselves.
Then when the time is right, things will fall into place. We will be together again, this time forever ❤
